{"tid":1246694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大港人支援反送中聯合行動（整合頁）","createTime":"2019-06-20T23:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:38:05.000Z","uid":259035,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb451713bba4ce7e24bb5f82729c2a166e9b48a","tid":1246694,"uid":259035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:46:03.000Z","msg":"加拿大港人支援反送中聯合行動（香港粵語）<br />\n <br />\n致所有加拿大香港人：<br />\n <br />\n由六月九日一百萬人遊行、六月十二日警民衝突，到六月十六日二百萬人群起上街反對《送中》修例，北京指派嘅特首林鄭月娥，對香港人嘅四大訴求係一件都無回應到：「撤回惡法修訂」、「收回暴動定性」、「追究濫用暴力」、「問責特首下台」，身為香港人，真係是可忍孰不可忍！<br />\n <br />\n雖然我哋已經移咗民去加拿大，但香港始終係我哋嘅家，三大城市溫哥華、多倫多同渥太華已經發起過兩次遊行聲援香港；不過林鄭依家玩拖延戰術，睇嚟我哋聲援都唔夠力，始終要有「實際行動」嚟升級！香港有成 30 萬加拿大籍港人，仲有 50 萬香港人住喺加拿大，總共  80 萬人嘅力量，加上支持人權同民主嘅本地朋友，足以影響執政聯邦自由黨正式出手，用各種手段向香港政權施壓，包括凍結官員及建制派議員在加海外資產，取消佢地同直系家屬嘅簽證，仲有撤消佢地申請加拿大國籍嘅資格，以維護香港人嘅基本人權同自由！<br />\n <br />\n以下係升級三部曲，非常簡單：<br />\n <br />\n1.     參加聯署<br />\n請透過以下連結簽名，聯署將會提交國會以及各聯邦政黨的國會議員。<br />\n（英文版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf8s9-7dWRT7BCtx44GGJNr5g8nJz8957U4Qyry9g_qkWn35w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf8s9-7dWRT7BCtx44GGJNr5g8nJz8957U4Qyry9g_qkWn35w%2Fviewform&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=ce2604d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf8s9-7dWRT7BCtx44GGJNr5g8nJz8957U4Qyry9g_qkWn35w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n（中文版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1_et-MQnUMT8jSrBRc2VsYOMtVqdWSzabTTcSkuJoHK0/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1_et-MQnUMT8jSrBRc2VsYOMtVqdWSzabTTcSkuJoHK0%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=b6ecec6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1_et-MQnUMT8jSrBRc2VsYOMtVqdWSzabTTcSkuJoHK0/viewform?edit_requested=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.     去信國會議員（MP）<br />\n有票，真係唔要？加拿大我地有真普選，手上一票可以決定邊一個黨執政。尤其十月大選在即，執政自由黨民調落後，我哋手上嘅選票佢哋一定好想要，所以我哋一定要畀呢啲國會議員（Members of Parliament）知道有大量選民關心呢件事！<br />\n<br />\n請電郵或郵寄（無需郵票）以下信件到所屬選區嘅國會議員：<br />\n重點議員：執政自由黨議員，尤其係佢哋嘅內閣成員、港裔、少數族裔嘅議員：<br />\n<br />\n內閣成員睇呢度：<a href=\"https://www.liberal.ca/cabinet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberal.ca%2Fcabinet%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=ab5d0869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.liberal.ca/cabinet/</a><br />\n其他重點成員睇呢度（如已聯署到其他MP的，請幫手加入）：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Uf-OFHaV49kh--NgQ4Q6mbbvrxu3qrqTMv9l6lTtUjw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Uf-OFHaV49kh--NgQ4Q6mbbvrxu3qrqTMv9l6lTtUjw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=5d871cb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Uf-OFHaV49kh--NgQ4Q6mbbvrxu3qrqTMv9l6lTtUjw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n信件Template如下（鍾意自己寫都得）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ykI64fucjzk1YyWqfC82MhgLabibGleB25W1HQu-YFk/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1ykI64fucjzk1YyWqfC82MhgLabibGleB25W1HQu-YFk%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e1a9ddc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ykI64fucjzk1YyWqfC82MhgLabibGleB25W1HQu-YFk/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔知自己所屬選區，可以用呢個 link搵返：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ourcommons.ca/Parliamentarians/en/constituencies/FindMP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourcommons.ca%2FParliamentarians%2Fen%2Fconstituencies%2FFindMP&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e5d9435e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ourcommons.ca/Parliamentarians/en/constituencies/FindMP</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.     約見國會議員<br />\n<br />\n寄完信其實唔夠㗎，要三五成群約見所屬選區嘅國會議員，兜口兜面催逼佢上達天庭先至得。可以搵埋你嘅隔離鄰舍，或者係呢個telegram group搵返同區嘅朋友：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KRmEzBXa6rTod6zOAtAmaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKRmEzBXa6rTod6zOAtAmaQ&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e92d61fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KRmEzBXa6rTod6zOAtAmaQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者，你可以喺下面嘅webform填寫你嘅email同埋postal code，我地嘗試幫你配對返同區嘅選民，一齊約見國會議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7guPiGfnjd9WrBz8F6oj0RgKSqiyM1-EwO6vnIhjJepHeuw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc7guPiGfnjd9WrBz8F6oj0RgKSqiyM1-EwO6vnIhjJepHeuw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e91d71a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7guPiGfnjd9WrBz8F6oj0RgKSqiyM1-EwO6vnIhjJepHeuw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於各議員嘅聯絡方式，可以用呢個 link 搵：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ourcommons.ca/Parliamentarians/en/constituencies/FindMP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourcommons.ca%2FParliamentarians%2Fen%2Fconstituencies%2FFindMP&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rang1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e5d9435e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ourcommons.ca/Parliamentarians/en/constituencies/FindMP</a><br />\n<br />\n坐言起行，一於下星期內做完上述三部曲，一齊向港共政權施壓，遙撐香港！"},{"pid":"8c965e7b159a20879a720b3e6b6d04952be297f6","tid":1246694,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"8aef55eb72778fdb7030abf2e0a913a86fd53f14","tid":1246694,"uid":196042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a86f71683bd5dd9d5bc89c6eb6953ac99d8f8c53","tid":1246694,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722ec9